========   Google Calendar Module v5.2.1.00.RC.4   ========
Created by Joe Curia (azumandias _ at _ hotmail.com)
Original phorum coding by the Phorum Development Team (http://www.phorum.org)

========        Brief Description         ========
This module allows visitors to submit a forum post to a Google calendar and 
allows the admin to show a seven day listing of events and/or to embed that 
calendar into the forum.

======== Installation/Usage Instructions  ========
Please refer to the Installation and Usage Guide which you can access from the 
top of this module's settings page or here:
http://trac.phorum.org/wiki/mods/google_calendar/installation_and_usage_guide

========              Notes               ========
This module is currently being released as a release candidate.  It is fully 
coded but has not been exhaustively tested.  Please feel free to use this 
module in a test environment and if you are willing to deal with some potential 
hassle you are welcome to use it in a production environment.

